This is the NEWS file for the x11vnc-auto package.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
v1.0.0 - 2/5/2019

Changes:

   Changed the VNC timeout to 30 seconds.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.9.1 - 3/30/2018

Changes:

   Modified the socket service to bind only IPv4.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.9.0 - 1/11/2018

Changes:

   Modified the service to run x11vnc(1) under user 'rd' rather than 'root'.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
